      <title>高盛表示，对冲基金借款触及五年来最高点</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-hedge-fund-borrowing-hits-five-year-peak-goldman-sachs-says-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛的一份报告显示，截至 4 月 19 日当周，全球对冲基金借款升至五年高位，对冲基金利用今年美国和欧洲股市首次大幅下跌的机会加大交易力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/hedge-flow-hedge-fund-borrowing-hits-five-year-peak-goldman-sachs-says-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 09:37:29 GMT</pubDate>
