      <title>瑞士央行提高银行最低准备金要求，降低利息成本</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/snb-raises-minimum-reserve-requirement-domestic-banks-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士国家银行（SNB）周一表示，正在提高国内银行的最低准备金要求，这​​可能每年为其节省数亿瑞士法郎的利息支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/europe/snb-raises-minimum-reserve-requirement-domestic-banks-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 06:39:43 GMT</pubDate>
